erning: none;\" style=\"font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">7. &nbsp; Bei Services mit einer Einwirkzeit (Zeit, in der der ausf&uuml;hrende Mitarbeiter verf&uuml;gbar ist),&nbsp;</span></span></p><p fr-original-style=\"margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000;\" style=\'margin: 0px; font: 11px \"Helvetica Neue\"; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\'><span fr-original-style=\"font-size: \r\n      14px;\" style=\"font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><span fr-original-style=\"font-kerning: none;\" style=\"font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; k&ouml;nnen Sie diese mit einem Klick auf &bdquo;Einwirkzeit hinzuf&uuml;gen&ldquo; festlegen</span></span></p><p fr-original-style=\"margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000;\" style=\'margin: 0px; font: 11px \"Helvetica Neue\"; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\'><span fr-original-style=\"font-kerning: none;\" style=\"font-kerning: none; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><br fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span></p><p fr-original-style=\"margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px \'Helvetica Neue\'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 12.0px;\" style=\'margin: 0px; font: 11px \"Helvetica Neue\"; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0); min-height: 12px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\'><br fr-original-style=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></p>', 'deleted', 1, '2020-04-14 12